{"type":"article","id":10473,"title":"那位反对香港法案和新疆法案的共和党众议员（Thomas Massie）发声了","uid":9580,"topics":[2973,28,330,17],"contents":"<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/R3dYKf.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/R3dYKf.png\" alt=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/R3dYKf.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n大意:“如果我国政府介入别国的内部事务，就相当于邀请别国政府也来干涉我国的内政。”<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/0Y7Nr1.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/0Y7Nr1.png\" alt=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/0Y7Nr1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n大意:（反对的人）是否能有实际行动，比如坚持一个星期拒买任何中国制造的产品。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nThomas Massie在此前制裁俄罗斯、伊朗、朝鲜的议案表决中，均投下了反对票。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nThomas Massie一贯反对美国对外干预其他国家的政策。","date":"2019-12-06","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":0}